text_content: Symphony Creative Studio is an AI-powered video generation tool that allows marketers to create TikTok-style videos in minutes. It leverages AI to generate video clips based on product descriptions, URLs, or existing assets. The tool can even pull images directly from a web to build videos that align with popular trends. Symphony Creative Studio is part of TikTok's Symphony creative AI suite.
